	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="With Karlach in your party, fight Gortash and defeat him.&#xD;&#xA;Using the origins debug book:&#xD;&#xA;1. Load BGO_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;2. Recruit Karlach&#xD;&#xA;3. Karlach -&gt; Gortash Confrontation -&gt; Kill Bodyguards&#xD;&#xA;4. Karlach -&gt; Gortash Confrontation -&gt; Teleport to Gortash&quot;&#xD;&#xA;5. Start fight and defeat Gortash" />
